data.value: Iif(True, '#NOT_SUPPORTED#', 'Shared numbervar WS_HISTORY_LATE; if {?gbNewAdd} then if {StatementCustomerHeader.NewBusiness} then "DEALER - " + {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER} + ChrW(13) + " " + {OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME} else Select {OPNHCUST.CUSTHIST_UPDATE_TYPE} Case "1": "DEALER - " + {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER} + ChrW(13) + " " + {OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ ChrW(13) + "YEAR BOOK" Case "2": "DEALER - " + {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER} + ChrW(13) + " " + {OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ ChrW(13) + "COOKWARE" Case "3": "DEALER - " + {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER} + ChrW(13) + " " + {OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ ChrW(13) + "BOOKS" Case "4": "DEALER - " + {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER} + ChrW(13) + " " + {OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ ChrW(13) + "ADD-ON AMOUNT" Case "5": "DEALER - " + {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER} + ChrW(13) + " " + {OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ ChrW(13) + "ANNUAL FEE" Default: "DEALER - " + {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER} + ChrW(13) + " " + {OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME} else Select {OPNHCUST.CUSTHIST_PAY_REM_1} Case "NEW ": {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER}+" "+{OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME} Case "LATE": ( WS_HISTORY_LATE := WS_HISTORY_LATE + {OPNHCUST.CUSTHIST_LATE_CHARGE}; "LATE CHARGE" ) Case "ADD ": Select {OPNHCUST.CUSTHIST_UPDATE_TYPE} Case "1": {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER}+" "+{OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ChrW (13)+"YEAR BOOK" Case "2": {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER}+" "+{OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ChrW (13)+"COOKWARE" Case "3": {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER}+" "+{OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ChrW (13)+"BOOKS" Case "4": {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER}+" "+{OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ChrW (13)+"ADD-ON AMOUNT" Case "5": {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER}+" "+{OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ChrW (13)+"ANNUAL FEE" Default: {OPNCUST.CUSTOMER_DEALER}+" "+{OPNDEALR.OPNDEALR_NAME}+ChrW (13) Default: UpperCase({PAYMENTTYPE.DESCRIPTION});')
